                  <span class="inline-block text-gray-400 text-sm"><time>April 05, 2022</time></span>
                </li>
              </ul>
                            <div class="addtoany_shortcode"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list" data-a2a-url="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/posts/3378/" data-a2a-title="Six Fashionable Sightseeing Spots Around Tokyo Station"><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjapanbusonline.com%2Fbus-repo%2Fposts%2F3378%2F&amp;linkname=Six%20Fashionable%20Sightseeing%20Spots%20Around%20Tokyo%20Station" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjapanbusonline.com%2Fbus-repo%2Fposts%2F3378%2F&amp;linkname=Six%20Fashionable%20Sightseeing%20Spots%20Around%20Tokyo%20Station" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjapanbusonline.com%2Fbus-repo%2Fposts%2F3378%2F&amp;linkname=Six%20Fashionable%20Sightseeing%20Spots%20Around%20Tokyo%20Station" title="Email" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save addtoany_share" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share"></a></div></div>              <div class="my-6 md:my-8">
                                  <div>
                    <p>There are so many things to do in Tokyo, I don't know where to go! If that's the case, we recommend the area around Tokyo Station. As well as the classic spots like the distinctive station building and the Imperial Palace, the area's sophisticated streetscape and exclusive shops are sure to win your heart!  Here are some fashionable sightseeing spots that girls who love Tokyo Station would like to recommend.</p>
                                          <img width="1999" height="1334" src="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image12.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image12.jpg 1999w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image12-300x200.jpg 300w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image12-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image12-768x513.jpg 768w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/image12-1536x1025.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px" />                                        <nav class="py-4 md:py-6 px-6 md:px-12 my-8 heading">
                      <h2 class="text-base text-center font-bold heading-ttl">Contents</h2>
                                              <ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><a href="#content-1"><strong><span style="font-weight: 400;">Six fashionable sightseeing spots around Tokyo Station</span></strong></a></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><a href="#headline-1"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tokyo Station Marunouchi Station Building with its beautiful retro red bricks</span></span></a></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><a href="#headline-2"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Feel the rich nature and history at Tokyo Imperial Palace</span></span></a></li>
